SENATE BILL 2374
By Rose
HOUSE BILL 2403
By Scarbrough
AN ACT to amend Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 33
and Title 39, relative to criminal justice.
BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF THE STATE OF TENNESSEE:
SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 39-13-530(j), is amended by adding
"speaker of the senate, speaker of the house of representatives," immediately after "civil justice
committee of the house of representatives".
SECTION 2. This act takes effect upon becoming a law, the public welfare requiring it.
